title: Tim Robards shirtless with brother James on Instagram
text:
He often flaunts his muscular physique in a number of shirtless snaps to Instagram .
But on Thursday, The Bachelor 's Tim Robards turned heads for another reason, drawing attention to his genetically-blessed younger brother James Robards, 22.
The 33-year-old shared a post-workout selfie with his hunky sibling in Sydney's Bondi, who is described as a 'hopeful marketing guru from Newcastle,' on his Instagram bio.
It's in the genes! The Bachelor's Tim Robards (left), 33, took to Instagram on Thursday, sharing a shirtless post-workout snap in Sydney's Bondi, with hunky brother James Robards (right), 22
'Arvo workouts and dip wiv me bruz (sic),' Tim began the caption.
'Intro'd him to the Bondi bars today...he looked like a bean pole before his session,' the former reality star continued.
The sweaty post-workout snap saw Tim standing next to his hunky brother in Sydney's Bondi, showing off their resemblance in facial features and physique.
Fans of Tim were quick to comment, with one writing: 'God dam that's some good genes,' while another posted: 'wow two hotties.'
Appeal: Fans of Tim were quick to comment, with one writing: 'God dam that's some good genes,' while another posted: 'wow two hotties'
Buff lads! Friendly competition sees the brothers comparing muscle definition, with one particular Instagram snap featuring the two flexing
This is not the first time James has made an appearance on his famous brother's social media account.
Several snaps see the genetically-blessed two working on their fitness, with James' bulging biceps, defined pecs and rippling abs on display.
Friendly competition also sees the brothers comparing muscle definition, with one particular Instagram snap featuring the two flexing.
In profile: A quick look on James' Instagram identifies the hunk as a 22-year-old 'hopeful marketing guru' from Newcastle in New South Wales
Sorry ladies! It also appears the personality is off the market, enjoying a long-term relationship with slender brunette Kirily Claut
A quick look on James' Instagram identifies the hunk as a 22-year-old 'hopeful marketing guru' from Newcastle in New South Wales.
Proud of his defined physique, numerous snaps see James shirtless, or in the gym showing off his bulging biceps.
It also appears the personality is off the market, enjoying a long-term relationship with slender brunette Kirily Claut.
A steamy snap saw James grabbing hold of Kirily's toned leg as she embraced her beau in an intimate moment.
Role model: It appears James is following in his famous brother's footsteps, making gym and working out a priority
